rows.name: We have assembled to discuss how best to proceed.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072602_MSG0002
rows.name:
But we've already waited an excessive amount of
time, and Sun'celeg has yet to arrive! What's become
of him?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072602_MSG0003
rows.name:
Lately, my Ovah has been astir over something.
Could this have been the cause?[ST:wait ]
